Package spoon.reflect.visitor

Class CtBiScannerDefault

java.lang.Object
spoon.reflect.visitor.CtAbstractVisitor
spoon.reflect.visitor.CtAbstractBiScanner
spoon.reflect.visitor.CtBiScannerDefault
All Implemented Interfaces:
CtVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
EqualsVisitor
public class CtBiScannerDefault extends CtAbstractBiScanner
This visitor implements a deep-search scan on the model for 2 elements. Ensures that all children nodes are visited once, a visit means three method calls, one call to "enter", one call to "exit" and one call to biScan. This class is generated automatically by the processor spoon.generating.CtBiScannerGenerator. Is used by EqualsVisitor.
